Bootstrap: localimage
From: ./ubuntu_22.04.sif

%post
    set -e

    # Update package lists and install Python plus pip
    apt-get update -y
    apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends python3 python3-pip

    # Install pytest for the forthcoming test-suite
    pip3 install --no-cache-dir pytest

    # ------------------------------------------------------------------
    # Prepare the directory structure and initial data files
    # ------------------------------------------------------------------
    # Create the home directory that the learner will work in
    mkdir -p /home/user
    chmod 0777 /home/user          # Make it writable for the non-root learner

    # Create the initial log file with the required contents
    cat > /home/user/db_queries.log <<'EOF'
1,1800,SELECT id, name FROM customers WHERE vip = true;
2,3050,UPDATE products SET stock = stock - 1 WHERE id = 987;
3,150,DELETE FROM sessions WHERE last_access < NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days';
4,4990,SELECT * FROM orders WHERE status = 'PENDING';
5,2400,INSERT INTO audit_log (event) VALUES ('user_login');
EOF

    # Ensure permissions are exactly 0644
    chmod 0644 /home/user/db_queries.log

%labels
    chmod 755 /home/user

    Author  ChatGPT
    Description  Environment for "optimize_slow_queries" task – initial state only.

%help
This Apptainer image sets up the initial filesystem state for the
“optimize_slow_queries” exercise. It installs Python, pytest, and
provides /home/user/db_queries.log with the required contents and
permissions. No solution script or report file is present; those will
be created by the learner.